RHEL 6, Install:
v.01
1. yum install mongodb-server
2. from the splice-repo install:
Django python-mongoengine python-kitchen django-tastypie django-tastypie-mongoengine python-kitchen \
pymongo-gridfs python-isodate
3. git clone git://github.com/jschrewe/django-mongodbforms.git
  * python setup.py install
4. from rpm or dev setup
  * install splice-server
  * install rhic-serve



